{"tid":984424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一樣都係自己靜落嚟既時候好容易亂諗野？","createTime":"2019-01-16T19:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T19:28:12.000Z","uid":33181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75919b03b3c925202015e8f56311272dc6cd4579","tid":984424,"uid":33181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:00:44.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊差唔多4個月 雖然同之前度算係不歡而散 因為佢男朋友長期唔理佢 但係有時出街有意無意都會聽到佢提起 其實個心會有啲唔舒服 但係唔知可以點表達 有冇人可以教下我應該點做先好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88e76a15dee6259ec10dfe6ac0ccc8a006d28d5","tid":984424,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},{"pid":"5d4727d187dde72b9f4982ed2d65e1aab4cb74d3","tid":984424,"uid":193314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88e76a15dee6259ec10dfe6ac0ccc8a006d28d5","tid":984424,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:05:45.000Z","msg":"做咩周圍留言分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed199edae935a2558dcceacd004cba872d4bf1f","tid":984424,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d4727d187dde72b9f4982ed2d65e1aab4cb74d3","tid":984424,"uid":193314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88e76a15dee6259ec10dfe6ac0ccc8a006d28d5","tid":984424,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:05:45.000Z","msg":"做咩周圍留言分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"等你留意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bo